<i>noun</i>: 푸념 [푸념], 투정 [투정] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>푸념 [푸념]</dt><br>
<dd>complaining; grumbling</dd><br>
<dd>마음속에 있는 불평을 늘어놓음. 또는 그런 말.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of talking about the complaints on one's mind, or such a remark.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>투정 [투정]</dt><br>
<dd>complaining; grumbling; growling</dd><br>
<dd>무엇이 모자라거나 마음에 들지 않아 떼를 쓰며 조르는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of badgering someone for more of something or for a new one, when something is in shortage or is not satisfactory.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>